org.phoenixbioinformatics.proxy.controller

Class Proxy.ProxyRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.phoenixbioinformatics.proxy.controller.Proxy.ProxyRequest
  • Enclosing class:
    Proxy

    private class Proxy.ProxyRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    A helper class that contains the proxy request information; you use this object to save an entire proxy request in the session for later execution, and this object allows for the decomposition of the processing methods. This includes information from the Http Request required to rewrite the response from the proxied server.
    Author:
    Robert J. Muller
